## Performance Comparison

```elixir
Benchee.run(
  %{
    "enum" => fn ->
      1..200
      |> Enum.map(fn each -> each * 2 end)
      |> Enum.filter(fn each -> each <= 10 end)
      |> Enum.take(4)
    end,
    "stream" => fn ->
      1..200
      |> Stream.map(fn each -> each * 2 end)
      |> Stream.filter(fn each -> each <= 10 end)
      |> Stream.take(4)
      |> Enum.to_list()
    end
  },
  memory_time: 2
)
```

